## What locking does now

```
Tap scan
    ↓
3 anchors placed per text block (triangle formation)
    ↓
Every frame: average 3 poses → measure drift
    ↓
BUILDING  → spinning cyan arc showing confidence %
    ↓ (~1s of stability)
CONFIRMING → full yellow ring pulsing "Locking…"
    ↓ (~0.5s more)
LOCKED    → green checkmark burst + double haptic pulse
            frozen matrix stored permanently
            anchors detached (no more ARCore drift)
            overlay switches from billboard → surface-aligned
            overlay never moves again
```

The key insight — **once locked, ARCore anchors are detached entirely**. The frozen matrix is stored in memory and rendered directly every frame. Nothing can move it.